  CRAN = 'https://cloud.r-project.org'
))

Define Helper Functions 

library(kwb.impetus)

get_master <- function(stations_df) {
  
  if ("Betreiber" %in% names(stations_df)) {
    stations_df <- stations_df %>% 
      dplyr::filter(.data$Betreiber == "Land Berlin") 
  }
  
  stations_df %>% 
    dplyr::pull(.data$stammdaten_link) %>%
    wasserportal::get_wasserportal_masters_data() %>% 
    dplyr::rename(Messstellennummer = .data$Nummer) %>% 
    dplyr::mutate(Messstellennummer = as.double(.data$Messstellennummer))
}

get_data_name <- function(para_name) {
  prefix <- ifelse(startsWith(para_name, "surface"), "daily_", "")
  paste0(prefix, para_name)
}

get_master_name <- function(para_name) {
  paste0("stations_", para_name)
}

label_river_km <- function(data) {
  sprintf(
    "%s (%s, id: %s, fluss-km: %2.2f)", 
    data$Name,
    data$Gewaesser, 
    data$Messstellennummer, 
    as.numeric(data$Flusskilometer)
  )
}

set_date_year_decade_month <- function(data) {
  data %>% 
    dplyr::mutate(
      Datum = as.Date(.data$Datum),
      Jahr = as.integer(format(.data$Datum, "%Y")), 
      Dekade = kwb.impetus::floor_decade(.data$Jahr),
      Dekade_Label = kwb.impetus::decade_label(.data$Dekade),
      Monat = as.factor(format(.data$Datum, "%m"))
    )
}

summarise_daily_mean_levels <- function(data) {
  variable <- "Tagesmittelwert_Pegelstand_mNN"
  data %>%
    dplyr::summarise(
      Monatsmittelwert_Pegelstand_mNN = mean(.data[[variable]]),
      q05 = kwb.impetus::numeric_quantile(.data[[variable]], 0.05),
      q95 = kwb.impetus::numeric_quantile(.data[[variable]], 0.95)
    )
}

summarise_to_monthly_means <- function(data, variable) {
  data %>%
    dplyr::summarise(
      Monatsmittelwert = mean(.data[[variable]]),
      q05 = kwb.impetus::numeric_quantile(.data[[variable]], 0.05),
      q95 = kwb.impetus::numeric_quantile(.data[[variable]], 0.95),
    )
}

summarise_daily_mean_values <- function(data) {
  summarise_to_monthly_means(data, variable = "Tagesmittelwert")
}

summarise_measurements <- function(data) {
  summarise_to_monthly_means(data, variable = "Messwert")
}

ggplot2_labels_monthly_mean <- function(what, title) { 
  ggplot2::labs(
    y = paste("Monatsmittel", what), 
    x = "Monatsnummer", 
    col = "Mittelwert", 
    fill = "5%/95% Konf.-intervall",
    title = title
  )
}

ggplot2_facet_wrap_decade <- function(ncol) {
  ggplot2::facet_wrap(~ .data$Dekade_Label, nrow = 1L, ncol = ncol)
}

ggplot2_theme <- function() {
  ggplot2::theme_bw() + 
    ggplot2::theme(legend.position = "bottom")
}

create_pdf_with_plots <- function(
    master_data, 
    summarise_fun, 
    y_column, 
    what, 
    file
) {
  
  master_data_agg <- master_data %>% 
    kwb.impetus::group_by_site_decade_month_label() %>% 
    summarise_fun()
  
  plots <- plot_for_all_sites(
    master_data_agg = master_data_agg,
    master_data = master_data,
    summarise_fun = summarise_fun,
    y_column = y_column,
    what = what
  )

  print_to_pdf(plots, file)
}

print_to_pdf <- function(plots, file) {
  
  kwb.utils::preparePdf(
    file,
    landscape = TRUE,
    width.cm = 29.7, 
    height.cm = 21
  )
  
  on.exit(dev.off())
  
  print(plots)
}

plot_for_all_sites <- function(
    master_data_agg, master_data, summarise_fun, y_column, what
) {
  
  decades <- kwb.impetus::decades_tibble(master_data_agg$Dekade_Label)

  ids <- unique(master_data_agg$Messstellennummer)

  lapply(ids, function(id) {
    
    p1 <- master_data_agg %>% 
      dplyr::filter(.data$Messstellennummer == id) 
    
    p2 <- master_data %>% 
      dplyr::filter(.data$Jahr == max(.data$Jahr)) %>% 
      kwb.impetus::group_by_site_year_month_label() %>% 
      summarise_fun() %>% 
      dplyr::filter(.data$Messstellennummer == id) 
    
    p1 %>% 
      ggplot2::ggplot(mapping = ggplot2::aes(
        x = as.integer(.data$Monat), 
        y = .data[[y_column]],
        col = as.factor(.data$Dekade_Label))
      ) + 
      #ggplot2::geom_point(alpha = 0.5) + 
      kwb.impetus::decade_ribbons() + 
      kwb.impetus::scale_fill_decades(decades) +
      kwb.impetus::scale_color_decades(decades) +
      ggplot2::geom_point() +
      ggplot2::geom_point(ggplot2::aes(
        x = as.integer(.data$Monat),
        y = .data[[y_column]]), 
        data = p2,
        col = "darkgrey",
        alpha = 0.5, 
        inherit.aes = FALSE,
        show.legend = FALSE
      ) +
      kwb.impetus::ggplot2_scale_x_continuous_12() +
      #ggplot2::geom_boxplot() +
      ggplot2_facet_wrap_decade(ncol = length(unique(p1$Dekade_Label))) +
      ggplot2_theme() + 
      ggplot2_labels_monthly_mean(what, title= unique(p1$Label))
  })
}

### otherwise rendering would last ~ 2 hours

wp_data <- wasserportal::wp_timeseries_data_to_list(overview_names)
### Alternatively: download latest data from Wasserportal Berlin (takes a while)

wp_gw_data <- wasserportal::get_groundwater_data(stations)
wp_data <- c(wp_sw_data, wp_gw_data)

Surface Water Level 

para_name <- "surface-water_water-level"

surfacewater_level_master <- wp_data %>%
  kwb.utils::selectElements(get_data_name(para_name)) %>% 
  dplyr::filter(.data$Parameter == "Wasserstand") %>%  
  set_date_year_decade_month() %>%
  dplyr::left_join(get_master(wp_master[[get_master_name(para_name)]])) %>% 
  dplyr::mutate(
    Tagesmittelwert_Pegelstand_mNN = as.numeric(.data$Pegelnullpunkt_m) +
      .data$Tagesmittelwert / 100
  ) %>%
  ### remove -777 for messstellennummer 5867000 (few values in 2000) 
  ### resulted by step above
  dplyr::filter(.data$Tagesmittelwert_Pegelstand_mNN != -777) %>%
  dplyr::select(- .data$Pegelnullpunkt_m) %>% 
  dplyr::mutate(Label = label_river_km(.data))
#> Importing 63 station metadata from Wasserportal Berlin ... ok. (36.21s)
#> Joining, by = "Messstellennummer"

create_pdf_with_plots(
  master_data = surfacewater_level_master,
  summarise_fun = summarise_daily_mean_levels,
  y_column = "Monatsmittelwert_Pegelstand_mNN",
  what = "Pegelstand (m NN)",
  file = "surface-water_level.pdf"
)
